 This is AVRGame project.
 
 Introduction:
============================

 AVRGame is a small, open source, and low const handheld game console based on
 AVR microcontroller. It works with 2 AA size battries, and have a 8x8 dot
 matrix display. Its joystick have 4 directional, and 1 fire/rotate push buttons.

