 AVRGame project contains the following files:
================================================
 Config.h
 Display.c
 Display.h
 Font.c
 Font.h
 Joystick.c
 Joystick.h
 Main.c
 Makefile
 Pong.c
 Pong.h
 README
 Schematic/AVR_game_demo.DSN
 Schematic/scan0001.jpg
 Tetris.c
 Tetris.h

 Known issues:
===============
  * No collision detection in down moving ball in Pong game.
  * Only buttom of tetromino collision detection in tetris game.

 Features:
===========
  * AVRGame is compatible with Codvision and gcc-avr compilers.
